r />\n就在楊康死後的月餘，穆念慈才發現自己有了身孕，便與黃蓉等人不告而別，消失於武林之中。<br />\n<br />\n一年的時間過去了，生產過後的穆念慈看著自己一歲的兒子，正赤裸裸地躺在床上，胯下的肉棒都顯得比起同年齡的小孩要來得大，明顯的是遺傳自父親，她俯上前去，張開小嘴含住後淫媚的上下吸吮著，小孩咯咯地笑了起來，肉棒也不斷地變大，穆念慈也開心地笑了起來，知道以後的自己，還是會有著性福的淫蕩生活！"},{"pid":"6d41b777b600395d9dca2c281bf5d2d403cff280","tid":298250,"uid":16281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:19:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dab6030c18817d6d2b2cd13c047915aa7545378","tid":298250,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"真係有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2cd1b71b97ebdadf19d249e91170430e9140e3","tid":298250,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢養父有冇試過同佢做愛</blockquote><br />\n冇點會養到佢咁大呀"},{"pid":"34728bb2c1d0a60e941db592dade770a7b776d5c","tid":298250,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"f7778c04db6bdc1cc566dd281137db7ace801a7d","tid":298250,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢養父有冇試過同佢做愛</blockquote><br />\n冇點會養到佢咁大呀</blockquote><br />\n等價交換黎"},{"pid":"c0224fd13b924b972ac4f755d3a9a8b6133153b3","tid":298250,"uid":54747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"時間一年一年的過去，楊過也慢慢的長大了，穆念慈看著越來越英俊的孩子，不禁感到欣喜，在一想到每晚自己趁兒子睡著後，用小嘴不斷吸吮他那粗大的肉棒，跨下那淫蕩的肉洞中不禁騷癢了起來，她知道，自己那每晚寂寞的淫豔胴體就要有人來滿足它了<br />\n<br />\n就在楊過15歲的這一年，穆念慈已被那高漲的慾火焚燒的不能自己了，每晚那淫蕩激烈的手淫再也不能滿足她強大的慾火了，她需要火熱粗大的肉棒來強猛的姦淫她，就在這個念頭下，穆念慈她決定要在今晚引誘楊過來幹她。"},{"pid":"01c887908aba5346d3ce1eff67f1da4470fdb989","tid":298250,"uid":8404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abd123c842801463b4ce544e0a5fea697878719","tid":298250,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"正當2人在享受時，郭伯伯進來了"},{"pid":"3d7c0eb046158d737171472a31cf7097a9093ed6","tid":298250,"uid":91454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正當2人在享受時，郭伯伯進來了</blockquote><br />\n當時穆念慈正騎在楊過身上不住搖動<br />\n楊過見狀正考量如何解釋<br />\n此時郭伯伯竟先開口問道<br />\n「到我了嗎？」<br />\n楊過還在狐疑，穆念慈已搶先答道<br />\n「前面在忙，你從後面來。」"},{"pid":"9c0ed5666c38b05cac8c7279b7536a95d138bf13","tid":298250,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:27:15.000Z","msg":"西毒二人都有同佢同船<br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"5f94e7111094d13c0fe036e75d09caa11f413645","tid":298250,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9359371f485942e53399d139ad6b9a359cd59c","tid":298250,"uid":115150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:23:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ba0b7823f128f88e5845388c27bbd8015da005","tid":298250,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ac189558896cd9d179704a7172b2962b757b4b","tid":298250,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"樓豬有沒唸過出鹽書幫熱狗籌旗牙"},{"pid":"63b71ed1929f920267f916d2187ccca062b8abe4","tid":298250,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cla